<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">Dear Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">Thank you for your email.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">As Megan mentioned in her response on 15 September 2025, the addit=
ional information you requested will be provided by
<b>8 October 2025</b>.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">Regarding the fees: we can only provide an estimate if you agree f=
or us to proceed with the additional work, which includes indexing by date,=
 author, short description, and system/location.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto">We will also review the redactions made and assess what can be don=
e to meet your request.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Warm rega=
rds<o:p></o:p></span></p>
